milestones.description: Jonty Rhodes and Cullinan's 232-run partnership is SA's highest for the 4th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 154 between Hansie Cronje and Gary Kirsten
Jonty Rhodes and Cullinan's 232-run partnership is the highest for the 4th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 173 between Dean Jones and Steve Waugh
This is the highest match aggregate (580) involving teams South Africa & Pakistan in ODIs
Jonty Rhodes and Cullinan's 232-run partnership is SA's highest for any wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 190 between Mike Rindel and Gary Kirsten
